
--!strict
-- KilometresUI V4
-- Single-file Roblox ModuleScript
-- Features:
--   • Draggable window
--   • Hide/show with draggable floating circle
--   • Animated toggles
--   • Settings panel
--   • Theme presets + accent presets
--   • Window placement presets
--   • Player avatar blueprint/profile card
--   • Buttons, toggles, sliders, dropdowns, boxes, labels, dividers
--   • Notifications

